snippet.title: Driver Oliver Rides a Taxi and Helps the City Rescuers
snippet.description:
Driver Oliver rides a taxi and helps the city rescuers - policemen, doctors and firefighters in difficult situations. Children learn and show how important it is to help each other in difficult cases.

00:00 Driver Oliver rides a taxi and helps the city rescuers
05:21 Diana and Roma show the Safety Rules on board the Airplane
09:57 Diana Roma and Oliver Explore the City on a Train Adventure
13:55 Diana and Roma teach School bus rules with friends
20:14 Let’s Buckle Up Story
23:00 Car Garage Adventure
